step-by-step guide
Login to your management console
go to s3 bucket
select create bucket, give a name and a region to host -> create bucket
upload your files and folders in the bucket
under properties enable website hosting (give the name of the initial file)
inside bucket permissions unblock public access
under bucket permissions enable ACL
select all the objects of the bucket that will be required for hosting and select actions-> make public using ACL 
